high_descs: Head across the kitchen to the sink.
Pick up the glass in the sink.
Bring the glass to the fridge on the right.
Chill the glass in the fridge.
Take the chilled glass to the opposite corner of the kitchen to the right by the wooden shelves.
Put the chilled glass on the middle wooden shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass on the middle wooden shelf.

high_descs: Go straight along the left side of the table, at the end of the table go straight and to right to the sink.
Take the glass from the sink.
Turn right, go to the fridge.
Put the glass on the bottom shelf of the fridge. Close then open the fridge door. Take the glass from the fridge.
Turn around, go straight to the oven, turn right, go straight and to the right to the brown shelves in the corner.
Put the glass on the left side of the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold glass on a shelf.

high_descs: Go straight then turn left, then move forward, then turn right, then move forward, then turn right, then left to go to the sink.
Take the glass from in the sink.
Turn around, go forward then turn left to the fridge.
Chill the glass inside of the fridge.
Turn around, then turn left, then turn right, then go straight to the shelf in the corner of the room, across from the trash can.
Place the glass on the middle shelf, towards the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass on the shelf.
